snippet.title: Granny (Trailer 2) Android and iOS
snippet.description:
Welcome to Granny´s house.

Granny keeps you locked in her house.
Now you have to try to get out of her house, but be careful and quiet. She hears everything.
If you drop something on the floor, she hears it and comes running.
You can hide in wardrobes or under beds.
You have 5 days.

Good luck!

Thank you for playing Granny!
And thank You all for 10000 subs :)

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dvloper.granny

App Store:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/granny/id1323957120

Granny's official website:
http://grannyhorror.com/
